snippet.title: The Elephant Collection Launch Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Say helloaphant to The Elephant Collection, a decology of John Cooney's iconic blue elephant games, lovingly remastered and restored for modern play!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2274110/The_Elephant_Collection/ 
Wishlist on GOG: https://www.gog.com/en/game/the_elephant_collection
Follow John Cooney on Twitter: https://twitter.com/jmtb02
